 mmwavelib_ffttwiddle_gen.cContains functions related to generate FFT twiddle factors. The functions are optimized for speed to allow quick reconfiguration when switching sub-frames in advanced frame mode. For FFT size less than or equal to 1024, the implementation is to store look-up table which is very high in memory consumption. For FFT size 2048, 4096, and 8192, the implementation is to use trigonometry formulas for interpolation from the look-up table
